nodes.text: A Dark Jedi was the daughter of a Duchess of Malastare. Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn later came to believe that the daughter's birth and status as a Dark Jedi meant that her mother was the subject of a prophecy in the Jedi holocron of prophecy about a female individual who would give birth to darkness after being born to darkness, as the Duchess' father had been known for waging vicious wars.
